    public class SequenceFileWriter<K extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable,V extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>
extends StreamWriterBase<org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple2<K,V>>
implements org.apache.flink.api.java.typeutils.InputTypeConfigurable
    A Writer that writes the bucket files as Hadoop SequenceFiles. The input to the RollingSink must be a Tuple2 of two Hadopo Writables.
